t: RA-NER: Retrieval augmented NER for knowledge intensive named entity recognition - Amazon Science
s: NER (named entity recognition) model aims to recognize the named entities in the keywords. However, when the entities are extremely knowledge intensive, traditional NER model cannot encode all the knowledge in its parameters, thus fails to recognize those entities with high accuracy.
